      "content": "but why is numbness worse than the exhaustion? if the end result is the same, the numbness feels like a mercy. constant struggle just feels like unnecessary pain. wouldn't it be more peaceful to just stop fighting and embrace the erasure? it feels like the only way to actually find some quiet.",
